{
  "stem": "22174.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, I worked there for 19 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after 17 or 18 years, I think it was, I had another heart attack, and a very, very, very almost fatal heart attack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I went back to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after two years, I was again close to another heart attack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a-- a neighbor persuaded me to have an-- have an open heart-- have open heart surgery, which I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But after a long talk with my wife, I-- I agreed to have it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So-- it was in the beginning where heart attacks wasn't that-- they're not like today, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I really-- I was tired.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was tired of life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That is true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But then after the talk with my wife, I-- I felt that she still needed me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I agreed to have the operation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And after the operation, I went back to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And two months later I was fired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Partly because I-- I had-- I couldn't work so much overtime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was still too tired, you know, from the operation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Partly because of that, but-- but more than that, more than that, was-- were the intrigues of my dear colleagues, my coworker who finally succeeded in having me fired.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
